{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my point is, in retrospect, I'm probably a damn fool to want to-- to-- to-- to feel like I missed out on something, because that's how you get killed is a skilled pilot with better skills or more training or more guts than you or more luck than you do, and that's how 40, 50% of the fighter pilots were killed by better pilots and better airplanes.",
      "word_count": 68
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I look back, and I think, I sure would like to have mixed it up with some more, but-- but being conservative and counting my blessings, it's-- I'm a lot better off because I didn't, because I probably would have got it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, who knows.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never thought about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never thought about dying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I-- it was just something I-- you know, it is not going to happen to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and it didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- but I came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there were guys who would say, you know, jeez, this is my 47th mission, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I'm about due.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And sometimes that would be our last mission, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And you'd think-- you have to pack up their stuff and send it home to their folks and write a letter, and oh it's-- But anyhow, so much for the aerial exploits of a guy who didn't get to do much of what he was trained to do the most.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's kind of the way I feel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "April comes, we were 10-- 12 of us from my unit were sent from the 10th fighter group-- were sent to Frankfurt to report to Seventh Army headquarters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Nobody told us what we were going to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We just packed our bags and-- and rode to Frankfurt on a-- on a truck.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
